import {Box,Spacer,Text,Image} from '@chakra-ui/react';
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom';


function MidPart1(){
    return(
        <Box style={{width:"85%",margin:"auto",padding:"15px",border:"1px solid deeppink"}}>
            <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row">
                <Box>
                    <Text  color="#666666" fontSize="1.6rem">Latest News & Videos</Text>
                </Box>
                <Spacer/>
                <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row" gap="3">
                    <Link to='/'></Link>
                    <Link to='/'></Link>
                    <Link to='/'></Link>
                    <Text>Save Lives with Your Blog</Text>
                    <Text>News & Articles</Text>
                    <Text>Follow Our Facebook</Text>
                </Box>
            </Box>
            <Box>

            </Box>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default MidPart1;
